###  http://www.semanticweb.org/issoc/ontologies/2026/3/untitled-ontology-9/correctiveActionTaken
<http://www.semanticweb.org/issoc/ontologies/2026/3/untitled-ontology-9/correctiveActionTaken> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty ;
                                                                                               rdfs:subPropertyOf owl:topDataProperty ;
