###  http://www.semanticweb.org/issoc/ontologies/2026/3/untitled-ontology-9/description
<http://www.semanticweb.org/issoc/ontologies/2026/3/untitled-ontology-9/description> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty ,
                                                                                              owl:FunctionalProperty ;
